Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳海校报的最新期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚出炉的最新版哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给我一份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 期末考试的对策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新期也很受欢迎嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为我们做了不少努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 卖完了 全部卖完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀嗬 这期的报纸也大受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 举办次宴会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上点心之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢 萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 银前辈去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计又在调戏女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个这篇报道有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实为了新闻部的照片材料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在招募美女模特 来试试看么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 不叫他也行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的敌人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 宴会要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去小卖部买点心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要饮料啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 放学后买齐这些东西带到社团室去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.02,0:01:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 来个BINGO大会之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.02,0:01:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}注：BINGO大会是指大家一起玩BINGO游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻部关系真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不明白啊 这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折皱了 你不嫌弃的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是月音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中更可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是谁啊 月音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不认识的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很让人觉得很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 别管了 今天放学后开大宴会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦——！
